      "date": "2012-10-05 22:15:40.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 1: I would prefer that you didn't submit this\n\nThis failed in ldiskfs testing, but only for the case where we are fiddling with the page itself to introduce checksum errors:\n\n07:31:35:Lustre: DEBUG MARKER: == sanity test 77g: checksum error on OST write ======================== 07:31:26 (1349447486)\n07:31:35:Lustre: DEBUG MARKER: lctl set_param fail_loc=0x8000021a\n07:31:35:Lustre: *** cfs_fail_loc=21a, val=0***\n07:31:35:LustreError: 4798:0:(ost_handler.c:1069:ost_brw_write()) client csum ef99b823, server csum 6c34b683\n07:31:35:BUG: Bad page state in process ll_ost_io00_003  pfn:496d3\n07:31:35:page:ffffea000100fe28 flags:0020000000000008 count:0 mapcount:0 mapping:ffff88007c37e850 index:0 (Not tainted)\n07:31:35:Pid: 4798, comm: ll_ost_io00_003 Not tainted 2.6.32-279.5.1.el6_lustre.ga194b25.x86_64 #1\n07:31:35:Call Trace:\n07:31:35: [<ffffffff81124ab7>] ? bad_page+0x107/0x160\n07:31:35: [<ffffffff81127b49>] ? free_hot_cold_page+0x1c9/0x220\n07:31:35: [<ffffffff81127c5f>] ? free_hot_page+0x2f/0x60\n07:31:35: [<ffffffff8112ab8e>] ? __put_single_page+0x1e/0x30\n07:31:35: [<ffffffff8112ad05>] ? put_page+0x25/0x40\n07:31:35: [<ffffffffa0c91801>] ? filter_commitrw_write+0x161/0x22e4 [obdfilter]\n07:31:35: [<ffffffffa0c859ad>] ? filter_commitrw+0x27d/0x2a0 [obdfilter]\n07:31:35: [<ffffffffa07a0be8>] ? obd_commitrw+0x128/0x3d0 [ost]\n07:31:35: [<ffffffffa07a77fc>] ? ost_brw_write+0xcfc/0x15d0 [ost]\n07:31:35: [<ffffffffa07ad6c2>] ? ost_handle+0x32e2/0x4690 [ost]\n07:31:35: [<ffffffffa082679c>] ? ptlrpc_server_handle_request+0x41c/0xe00 [ptlrpc]\n07:31:35: [<ffffffffa0827d71>] ? ptlrpc_main+0xbf1/0x19e0 [ptlrpc]",
